title: Adam Friedland Challenges Destiny TO A DUEL?
description:
Adam Friedland calls in to a Destiny stream to throw down the debate gauntlet and formally challenge him in the marketplace of ideas. This is after Destiny got upset seeing himself get roasted on a clip from The Adam Friedland Show inspired by Divorcestiny lore from Hasan Piker.
